<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink345">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>putuppū vatira ṟāayk</l>
<l>katuppaṟa laṇiyuṅ kāmar poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived,  </l>
<l>when jasmine spreads fresh flowers </l>
<l>and adorns black sand, [as if it was] hair. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
